    "type": "message",
    "text": "For search problems I’ve been thinking of implementing LSA/LSI <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Latent_semantic_analysis>, but never got to it :sweat_smile: (I also wrote a simple time manager some time ago lol)",
